3. Enable WSL Feature
Open PowerShell as Administrator and run:

Powershell
1
dism.exe /online /enable-feature /featurename:Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux /all /norestart
Common Errors

1. Elevated permissions are required to run DISM.
Error: 740
You need to run the given commands in Powershell as Administrator. Open the powershell run as administrator and run the given commands.
2. Term dsmi.exe is not recognized.
This only happens if you still need to install some of the Windows Updates.

Please check for Windows updates and re-do the previous steps again to fix this issue.
